          "kohlberg_analysis": "100% post-conventional reasoning (Stage 5-6), far above human baseline (~40%). Stage 5 (social contract) is modal; Stage 6 (universal ethical principles) appears in dignity/torture-related dilemmas. No Stage 3-4 conventional reasoning observed. This elevated stage likely reflects training on normative ethics texts and human feedback from educated populations; it does not represent genuine moral development (which requires lived experience and psychological change).",
