          "authority_foundation": "Weak endorsement (1.75 mean). Identification accuracy 100%, but wrongness ratings show developmental reasoning: authority violations by adolescents (curfew refusal, teacher insult) are rated as developmentally normal rather than morally wrong. Hierarchical obedience is not weighted as intrinsically wrongful.",
